{"article_id":"Ky6bsUIcBKu6Nt3o","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The Democratic National Convention kicked off Monday","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"without its outgoing Democratic National Committee chairwoman , Debbie Wasserman Schultz ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"following a chaotic scene at a morning meeting","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"where she was loudly jeered by Bernie Sanders supporters .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"`` I have decided","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that in the interest","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"of making sure","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"that we can start the Democratic convention on a high note","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"that I am not going to gavel in the convention , ''","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Wasserman Schultz told the Sun Sentinel newspaper in an interview .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Baltimore Mayor Stephanie Rawlings-Blake ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"who is also the Democratic National Committee 's secretary ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"handled the gaveling instead .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"`` Delegates , alternatives , standing committee members and all of our honored Democrats and other guests here in Philadelphia and all of you","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"who have joined us by television , radio and online , here in the United States and around the world , ''","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"she said ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"`` I hereby call the 47th quadrennial Democratic National Convention to order . ''","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Wasserman Schultz will also not speak tonight or throughout the duration of the convention ,","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"a Democrat close to her says .","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"She will remain in Philadelphia until Friday","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"when she formally steps down as leader of the committee .","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"Wasserman Schultz changed her plans","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"as the fallout deepened from leaked DNC emails","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"that appeared to show the committee","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"favoring presumptive Democratic nominee Hillary Clinton over Sanders during the primary .","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"It became clear Monday that the convention floor could erupt in anger","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"if she gaveled the convention into session","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"or sought to speak .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"And the Democratic National Committee issued an apology to Sanders","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"moments after the convention opened ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"likely hoping to help soothe tensions heading into the week .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"`` On behalf of everyone at the DNC , we want to offer a deep and sincere apology to Sen. Sanders , his supporters , and the entire Democratic Party for the inexcusable remarks","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"made over email , ''","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"the statement said .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"`` These comments do not reflect the values of the DNC or our steadfast commitment to neutrality during the nominating process .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"The DNC does not","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"-- and will not --","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"tolerate disrespectful language","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"exhibited toward our candidates .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Individual staffers have also rightfully apologized for their comments ,","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"and the DNC is taking appropriate action","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"to ensure","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"it never happens again . ''","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"The morning Florida delegate meeting descended into chaos","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"when Wasserman Schultz took the stage ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"with critics holding up signs with the word `` emails , ''","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"and Sanders supporters booing the congresswoman loudly ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"even after she began speaking .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"`` We have to make sure","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"that we move forward together in a unified way , ''","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Wasserman Schultz said during brief remarks .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"`` We know","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"that the voices in this room","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"that are standing up","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"and being disruptive ,","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"we know","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"that is not the Florida","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"that we know .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"The Florida","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"that we know","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"is going to make sure","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"that we continue to make jobs . ''","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"The audience was roughly half supportive of Wasserman Schultz and half detractors ,","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"though the angry participants were louder than the other half .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"Those attendees began to chant , `` Shame ! Shame ! Shame ! ''","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"while Wasserman Schultz was speaking .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"Sanders tried to quell some of his dissatisfied supporters at a rally before his expected speech Monday .","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"`` We have got to elect Hillary Clinton and Tim Kaine , ''","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"Sanders said ,","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"which prompted some attendees to shout him down .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Sanders booed","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"after voicing support for Clinton","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Sanders booed","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"after voicing support for Clinton","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"01:18","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"Wasserman Schultz announced Sunday","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"she is stepping down as chairwoman of the DNC at the end of the party 's convention .","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"The drama reinforced concerns about Democratic party unity .","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"Former Sanders campaign manager Jeff Weaver tried to show a unified Democratic Party on Monday , the morning","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"after Wasserman Schultz announced her resignation .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"`` This happened ,","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"we knew","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"it happened then ,","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"now is the time","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"to go forward , '","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"Weaver told CNN 's Chris Cuomo on `` New Day '' on Monday .","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"`` Now is the time","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"to elect Hillary Clinton","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"and defeat Donald Trump . ''","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"Wasserman Schultz talked with both President Barack Obama and Clinton","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"before making announcing her upcoming resignation ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"a Democratic source said .","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"`` Going forward , the best way for me","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"to accomplish those goals","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"[ which include electing Clinton president ]","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"is to step down as Party Chair at the end of this convention , ''","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"Wasserman Schultz said in the statement .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"`` As party chair , this week I will open and close the Convention","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"and I will address our delegates about the stakes","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"involved in this election","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"not only for Democrats , but for all Americans , ''","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"Sanders campaign manager :","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"We must elect Clinton","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"Sanders campaign manager :","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"We must elect Clinton","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"00:56","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"DNC Vice Chairwoman Donna Brazile will serve as interim chair through the election .","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"She had been a CNN political commentator ,","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"but CNN and Brazile have mutually agreed to suspend their contract , effective immediately ,","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"although she will remain on air during the convention week in an unpaid capacity ,","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"CNN said .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"CNN will revisit the contract","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"once Brazile concludes her role .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"Separately , a Democratic operative said","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"Hispanic leaders close to Clinton and her high command were discussing Housing Secretary Julian Castro as a possible successor to Wasserman Schultz at the DNC helm , among a number of other candidates","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"whose name are being mentioned .","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"Chants of `` Debbie is done ! ''","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"and `` Debbie resigned ! ''","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"broke out at a pro-Sanders rally Sunday in Philadelphia","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"after the news was announced .","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"Party officials decided Saturday","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"that Wasserman Schultz would not have a major speaking role or preside over daily convention proceedings this week .","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"The DNC Rules Committee has named Rep. Marcia Fudge , D-Ohio , as permanent chair of the convention ,","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"according to a DNC source .","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"She will gavel each session to order","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"and will gavel each session closed .","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"`` She 's been quarantined , ''","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"another top Democrat said of Wasserman Schultz ,","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"following a meeting Saturday night","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"but before her announcement","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"that she was leaving .","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"Obama issued a statement ,","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"saying ,","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"`` For the last eight years , Chairwoman Debbie Wasserman Schultz has had my back .","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"This afternoon , I called her","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"to let her know","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"that I am grateful . ''","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"And Clinton thanked Wasserman Schultz for her leadership of the party .","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"`` I am grateful to Debbie","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"for getting the Democratic Party to this year 's historic convention in Philadelphia ,","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"and I know","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"that this week 's events will be a success","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"thanks to her hard work and leadership , ''","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"Clinton said .","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"After slamming Wasserman Schultz as `` highly overrated , ''","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"Trump ,","depth":14},{"id":154,"text":"speaking at a rally in Roanoke , Virginia ,","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"knocked Clinton for being disloyal to the soon-to-be former DNC chair .","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"`` How about that for disloyalty in terms of Hillary Clinton .","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"Because Debbie Wasserman Schultz has been so much for Hillary Clinton , ''","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"Trump said .","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"`` These politicians .","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"There 's no loyalty there .","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"No loyalty .","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"None whatsoever . ''","depth":14},{"id":163,"text":"`` It gets a little heat","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"and they fire her , ''","depth":14},{"id":165,"text":"Trump said .","depth":13},{"id":166,"text":"`` Debbie was totally loyal to Hillary","depth":13},{"id":167,"text":"and Hillary threw her under a bus","depth":14},{"id":168,"text":"and it did n't take more than five minutes","depth":15},{"id":169,"text":"to make that decision . ''","depth":15},{"id":170,"text":"Wasserman 's Republican counterpart , Reince Priebus , said ,","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"`` I think","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"the day 's events show really the uphill climb","depth":14},{"id":173,"text":"Democrats face this week . ''","depth":14},{"id":174,"text":"`` The extreme left will not be satisfied by one person 's resignation , ''","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"the Republican party national chairman added .","depth":13},{"id":176,"text":"Trump campaign chairman Paul Manafort said","depth":14},{"id":177,"text":"Clinton should follow Wasserman Schultz out the door .","depth":14},{"id":178,"text":"`` Debbie Wasserman Schultz resigned over her failure","depth":16},{"id":179,"text":"to secure the DNC 's email servers and the rigged system","depth":17},{"id":180,"text":"she set up with the Clinton campaign , ''","depth":17},{"id":181,"text":"he said in a statement .","depth":15},{"id":182,"text":"`` Now Hillary Clinton should follow Wasserman Schultz 's lead","depth":15},{"id":183,"text":"and drop out over her failure","depth":16},{"id":184,"text":"to safeguard top secret , classified information both on her unauthorized home server and while traveling abroad . ''","depth":16},{"id":185,"text":"Weaver called Wasserman Schultz 's departure a win on CNN 's `` Erin Burnett OutFront '' on Sunday .","depth":13},{"id":186,"text":"`` I think","depth":16},{"id":187,"text":"what the signal was today is that the voices of Bernie Sanders supporters have been heard , ''","depth":16},{"id":188,"text":"he said .","depth":15},{"id":189,"text":"`` And other people , frankly , in the party , Hillary Clinton supporters ,","depth":17},{"id":190,"text":"who felt","depth":18},{"id":191,"text":"this was the last straw ,","depth":19},{"id":192,"text":"that she had to go ,","depth":19},{"id":193,"text":"and this shows","depth":17},{"id":194,"text":"they have been heard","depth":17},{"id":195,"text":"and gives us opportunity","depth":16},{"id":196,"text":"to move forward toward November","depth":17},{"id":197,"text":"-- united","depth":18},{"id":198,"text":"to deal with the problem of Donald Trump . ''","depth":18},{"id":199,"text":"Wasserman Schultz 's stewardship of the DNC has been under fire through most of the presidential primary process ,","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"but her removal from the convention stage comes","depth":14},{"id":201,"text":"following the release of nearly 20,000 emails .","depth":14},{"id":202,"text":"One email appears to show DNC staffers","depth":15},{"id":203,"text":"asking how they can reference Sanders ' faith","depth":16},{"id":204,"text":"to weaken him in the eyes of Southern voters .","depth":16},{"id":205,"text":"Another seems to depict an attorney","depth":15},{"id":206,"text":"advising the committee on how to defend Clinton against an accusation by the Sanders campaign","depth":16},{"id":207,"text":"of not living up to a joint fundraising agreement .","depth":16},{"id":208,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":6},{"id":209,"text":"Sanders :","depth":7},{"id":210,"text":"No question","depth":8},{"id":211,"text":"DNC was supporting Hillary Clinton","depth":8},{"id":212,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":213,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":9},{"id":214,"text":"Sanders :","depth":10},{"id":215,"text":"No question","depth":11},{"id":216,"text":"DNC was supporting Hillary Clinton","depth":11},{"id":217,"text":"02:08","depth":8},{"id":218,"text":"Before the announcement , Sanders on Sunday told Tapper","depth":9},{"id":219,"text":"the release of the DNC emails","depth":12},{"id":220,"text":"that show","depth":13},{"id":221,"text":"its staffers","depth":14},{"id":222,"text":"working against him","depth":14},{"id":223,"text":"underscores the position","depth":12},{"id":224,"text":"he 's held for months :","depth":12},{"id":225,"text":"Wasserman Schultz needs to go .","depth":10},{"id":226,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":10},{"id":227,"text":"she is qualified to be the chair of the DNC , not only for these awful emails ,","depth":12},{"id":228,"text":"which revealed the prejudice of the DNC ,","depth":12},{"id":229,"text":"but also because we need a party","depth":13},{"id":230,"text":"that reaches out to working people and young people ,","depth":13},{"id":231,"text":"and I do n't think","depth":13},{"id":232,"text":"her leadership style is doing that , ''","depth":13},{"id":233,"text":"Sanders told Tapper on `` State of the Union , '' on the eve of the Democratic National Convention in Philadelphia .","depth":9},{"id":234,"text":"`` I am not an atheist , ''","depth":10},{"id":235,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":236,"text":"`` But aside from all of that , it is an outrage and sad that you would have people in important positions in the DNC","depth":10},{"id":237,"text":"trying to undermine my campaign .","depth":10},{"id":238,"text":"It goes without saying :","depth":10},{"id":239,"text":"The function of the DNC is to represent all of the candidates","depth":11},{"id":240,"text":"-- to be fair and even-minded . ''","depth":11},{"id":241,"text":"He added :","depth":10},{"id":242,"text":"`` But again , we discussed this many , many months ago , on this show ,","depth":11},{"id":243,"text":"so what is revealed now is not a shock to me . ''","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":487,"left":0,"right":486,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":486,"left":313,"right":485,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":313,"left":286,"right":312,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":271,"right":285,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},